::Killfest/Scyther/Demise/Greven/EndBringer::

Killfest enters the tunnel, remembering something and acivating his 
comm.

"Scyther, get back here," he says into it, "I'll need you for this 
mission."

He turns around, following Darkfate through the tunnel.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Just outside the cave, Scyther turns around and enters it again, 
following Killfest into the tunnel. He knew what he would be needed 
for on this mission Killfest had planned for him.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Demise, Greven, and EndBringer continue on toward the new ship.
